{"type":"message","id":"3929458e","parentId":"0864fb5b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:45:05.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Alright, let me break this down:\n\n1. This is a cron job for \"Tobias Task Watchdog\"\n2. I need to read `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md` for context\n3. Execute `python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py`\n4. Inspect the JSON output\n5. Key rule: if `notifications` is empty, reply with EXACTLY `NO_REPLY` and nothing else\n6. If there are notifications, rewrite them in clean Portuguese, concise but informative\n7. Don't send silent confirmations\n8. Don't explain empty scans\n9. Don't invent status\n\nLet me start by reading the README to understand what this watchdog does.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"I'll read the watchdog README first, then execute it."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01LQjoU7UBCAYs6Qz2ApAuno","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":278,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":740,"totalTokens":16667,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0013900000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.000925,"total":0.0038889000000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774809902994,"responseId":"msg_01AnT1ScwsK1xuaBqJDjMwic"}}
